edu.vt.api.eatstreet.model.user

Class CreditCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.vt.api.eatstreet.model.EatStreetModel
      • edu.vt.api.eatstreet.model.user.CreditCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CreditCard
extends EatStreetModel
implements java.io.Serializable
    This model class represents a user's credit card. Some example code: 
    
 // Create a new card
 CreditCard card = new CreditCard();
 card.setCardholderName("John Doe");
 card.setCardholderStreetAddress("1234 Example Lane, Blacksburg, VA");
 card.setCardholderZip("24060");
 card.setCardNumber("1234123412341234");
 card.setCvv("123");

        public boolean equals(java.lang.Object other)
